  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Whenever you cast a conjuration (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Conjuration\" rel=\"nofollow\">summoning</a>) spell, increase the duration by a number of rounds equal to 1/2 your wizard level (minimum 1). This increase is not doubled by @Compendium[pf1.feats.btXWioB3SKJv8YEG]{Extend Spell}. At 20th level, you can change the duration of all&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/s/summon-monster\" rel=\"nofollow\">summon monster</a>&nbsp;spells to permanent. You can have no more than one&nbsp;summon monster&nbsp;spell made permanent in this way at one time. If you designate another&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/s/summon-monster\" rel=\"nofollow\">summon monster</a>&nbsp;spell as permanent, the previous spell immediately ends.</p>"
    },
